Package: MetaComp
Version: 1.0.1
Title: Tools for Merging and Visualization of EDGE (GOTTCHA, BWA, Kraken, MetaPhlAn) Taxonomy Assignments
Description: Implements routines for taxonomy assignments collection, aggregation, and visualization. 
Outputs SVG and PDF heatmap plots representing a comparison of taxa abundances across projects. 
Authors@R: person("Pavel", "Senin", , "psenin@lanl.gov", c("aut", "cre"))
